reviewText: is this how loyal fans are appreciated by idiot ,greedy networks?. the pretender another brilliant successful series cancelled without any  logical reason. this is totaly rediculious and insulting. what is the point of making a series and not having a conclusive ending . at the end of the day the fans have actualy wasted their time following the series. it is like watching a movie without being able to see the end.warning!!! if you have not seen this series yet , and although it has an exellent and intriguing plot , it would be a waste of time buying and viewing it as it has no "real" conclusive ending .(final episode ends on a rediculious cliffhanger).this was followed by two tv movies ,but still did not thoroughly conclude the story.the two tv movies have left the story even more inconclusive.
summary: yet another good series ruined by clif hanger and non conclusive so called ending!!!.

reviewText: ok wellwhile living in Italy they used to show this at around dinner time everyday, and everyday i would watch it.I loved the showBut now watching like 3 or 4 episodes in a row, its hard :P It gets really boring and repetetive while if u just watched one a day you wouldnt really notice this.Its one of those tv shows popular in the 90's, the monster-of-the-week type where the show would have some continuity but every episode would have a different plot and not follow straight from the previous episode like many night time soap operas nowadays :Lost,Grey's Anatomy and Desperate Houewives.The style of the show reminds me of the X-files, as Jarod sis trying to bring some1 to justice he would find out more about his past.

reviewText: This a good series but have 2 movies to add on the collection, but the truth is that you never going to have the whole story because the producers never do it one, its incomplete.  This is the most sadness and hopeless story I ever watch. I mean it. The story is good but with to many secrets, many struggles and leave the audience in the middle of nowhere. Even so, the characters are good especially Miss Parker. It's sad to watch a good story died with nothing to says. I dream for a third movie for years but its silly at this time. Most of 10 years are past and nothing happen.  So sad...
summary: Good Story but Incomplete...this really need an ending :(
